          p.info Share your iPhone's homescreen with the world and inspire. Share your iPhone's homescreen.

        section.box
          p.title
            ' Secure
            span.icon j
          p.info Share your iPhone's homescreen with the world and inspire. Share your iPhone's homescreen.

        section.box
          p.title
            ' Download
            span.icon H
          p.info Share your iPhone's homescreen with the world and inspire. Share your iPhone's homescreen.

        section.boxnomargin
          p.title
            ' Purchase
            span.icon d
          p.info Share your iPhone's homescreen with the world and inspire. Share your iPhone's homescreen.

        section.box
          p.title
            ' Customize
            span.icon P
          p.info Share your iPhone's homescreen with the world and inspire. Share your iPhone's homescreen.

        section.box
